text: Florence Sancroft (30 December 1902 - 22 January 1978) was a British swimmer. She competed in the women's 300 metre freestyle event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1978 deaths Category:British female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London Category:Female freestyle swimmers
